name: Parity
title: Parity
purpose: (Clinical Focus: This set of  values contains physical exam finding that represent the number of live deliveries the patient experienced prior to current hospitalization.),(Data Element Scope: The intent of this data element is to identify the number of live deliveries the patient experienced prior to current hospitalization.  Using the Quality Data Model, this particular element will map to the "Assessment" category.),(Inclusion Criteria: Include SNOMED CT codes that identify the number of live deliveries the patient experienced prior to current hospitalization.),(Exclusion Criteria: Exclude codes that do not meet the inclusion criteria.)
